window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The crossover event to end all crossovers!</b></p> <p><i>One night. Seven couples. A Christmas they’ll never forget.</i></p> <p><i>Jingle Bell Rock</i> features seven couples from across the Ella and Brooke universe, all coming together in one story to bring you joy, happiness, and a little Christmas cheer.</p> <p>Featuring:</p> <p>Logan &amp; Tate (Temptation Series)</p> <p>Ace &amp; Dylan (Preslocke Series)</p> <p>Viper &amp; Halo (Fallen Angel Series)</p> <p>Robbie, Julien, &amp; Priest (Confessions Series)</p> <p>Panther &amp; Solo (Elite Series)</p> <p>Shaw &amp; Trent (South Haven Series)</p> <p>Paige &amp; Dawson w/Ryleigh (LA Liaisons Series)</p>"; 
